ss=\"fn\">a</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The normalized factors of a polynomial over a field times its leading coefficient give\nthe polynomial.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Polynomial/FieldDivision.html#Polynomial.leadingCoeff_mul_prod_normalizedFactors","kind":"theorem","line":701,"name":"Polynomial.leadingCoeff_mul_prod_normalizedFactors","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Algebra/Polynomial/FieldDivision.lean#L701-L711"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Polynomial/FieldDivision.html#Polynomial.irreducible_iff_lt_natDegree_lt\"><span class=\"name\">Polynomial</span>.<span class=\"name\">irreducible_iff_lt_natDegree_lt</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">R</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Field/Defs.html#Field\">Field</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Polynomial/Basic.html#Polynomial\">Polynomial</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hp0</span> : <span class=\"fn\">p</span> <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Ne\">≠</a> <span class=\"fn\">0</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hpu</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Not\">¬</a><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Units/Defs.html#IsUnit\">IsUnit</a> <span class=\"fn\">p</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div cl