fs.html#Polynomial.natDegree\">natDegree</a></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HDiv.hDiv\">/</a> <span class=\"fn\">2</span>)</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">q</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Dvd.dvd\">∣</a> <span class=\"fn\">p</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Units/Defs.html#IsUnit\">IsUnit</a> <span class=\"fn\">q</span></span></span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"To check a polynomial over a field is irreducible, it suffices to check only for\ndivisors that have smaller degree.\n\nSee also: `Polynomial.Monic.irreducible_iff_natDegree`.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Polynomial/FieldDivision.html#Polynomial.irreducible_iff_degree_lt","kind":"theorem","line":670,"name":"Polynomial.irreducible_iff_degree_lt","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Algebra/Polynomial/FieldDivision.lean#L670-L681"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Polynomial/FieldDivision.html#Polynomial.isCoprime_of_is_root_of_eval_derivative_ne_zero\"><span class=\"name\">Polynomial</span>.<span class=\"name\">isCoprime_of_is_root_of_eval_derivative_ne_zero</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">K</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Field/Defs.html#Field\">Field</a> <span class=\"fn\">K</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Polynomial/Basic.html#Polynomial\">Polynomial</a> <span class=\"fn\">K</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=